<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078636" n="1r"/>
<opener><salute>Vir Doctissime et Celeberrime.</salute></opener>
  <p>Quoniam frustra hactenus expectavi responsum ad binas <rs key="B_991170515020405501 B_991170515020305501" type="letters">meas literas</rs>
<lb/>quas ad te pervenire curavi, quasque <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergomo</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basil<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>am</rs> certo certius
                    <lb/>fuisse transmissas ab Amico meo<!-- persontag --> intelligo, unam adhuc ad te mit<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tere epistolam<note type="editorial">Meint vorliegenden Brief.</note> decerno; qua equidem rogo Dominationem tuam
    <lb/>ut saltem me admoneas num meas acceperis literas, et an <rs key="B_991170517054405501 B_991170517054205501" type="letters">meas</rs>
<lb/>acceperit <choice><abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Dominus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus</rs> Nepos tuus doctissimus. Iis epistolis plura tibi et <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>poti</rs> dicebam de Mathematum <rs type="organisation">Cathedra</rs>, ad quam implendam
                    <lb/>te advocabunt, si voles, <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice>  Patavini <rs type="organisation">Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>i</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderat<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ores</rs> promittentes post tres circiter annos promotionem ad
    <lb/>eandem <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> eiusdem <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nepotis</rs> tui. Si <rs key="B_991170515020405501 B_991170515020305501" type="letters">meas literas</rs>
<lb/>te non accepisse intelligam, denu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> scribam ea qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in iisdem contineban<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum scias cupio, me esse semper paratissimum ad man<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>data tua; et necessum esse ut mihi scribas epistolam, quam possim
                    <lb/>ostendere <choice><abbr>Nobiliss:<hi rend="sup">is</hi></abbr><expan>Nobilissimis</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatoribus</rs>, quaque exponas tuam volunta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem, stipendium quod tibi lubet petendo, aut proponendo tui loco
                    <lb/><choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimum</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nepotem</rs> tuum, cui non paucum adfert damnum maxi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ma tui fama. Cit<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> responsione opus est, alioquin long<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> dilatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ne <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> amittemus, ad quam plures profect<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> te longe inferiores con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>currunt.</p>
<p>Sicuti ego te et <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nepotem</rs> tuum magnifacio, ita vellem ut tu, aut ipse
                    <lb/>veniret <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> ad Mathematicas disciplinas edocendas; quamobrem mea
                    <lb/>interponam officia (quod etiam hactenus feci) ut vestrum unus aut
                    <lb/>alter promoveatur. Tui promotio, si tibi placebit, erit certissima.</p> <p>Rogo autem bonitatem tuam ut mihi communices methodum pro mensuran<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dis, et dignoscendis fluidis crassioribus, et subtilioribus, et eodem tempore mihi assi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gnes differentiam intimam, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> fluidum crassius ex. gr. oleum distingui<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> fluido subtiliori <choice><abbr>v.</abbr><expan>verbi</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>gr.</abbr><expan>gratia</expan></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>; sive ut mihi significes in quibus consis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tat crassities, et subtilitas fluidorum in genere. Datis in aliquo canali flui<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dis divers<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> crassitiei, oleo <choice><abbr>v.</abbr><expan>verbi</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>gr.</abbr><expan>gratia</expan></choice> et aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>, simul et eodem tempore per
                        <pb facs="1078637" n="1v"/>
<lb/>eius sectionem quacunque vi fluentibus, datisve in ali<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>qua a principio motus fluidorum distantia, in superficie eiusdem
                        <lb/>canalis duobus poris, sive orificiis lateralibus diversarum diametrorum
                        <lb/>per qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fluida fluentia possint exire. Annon orificium illud late<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rale, per quod oleum effluere nequit, effluit vero aqua, erit mino<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ris diametri respectu alterius orificii, per quod potest oleum non
                        <lb/>solum effluere ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m etiam aqua? Annon quia oleum effluere ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quit per illud orificium laterale, per quod aqua potest effluere,
                        <lb/>olei particul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> minim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> componentes diametros habent maiores
                        <lb/>diametris particularum minimarum aquam componentium?
                        <lb/>Annon datis duobus fluidis, quorum unum potest devolvi in dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>diametri poros, aliud ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> per eosdem poros derivari non potest,
                        <lb/>illud dicetur fluidum crassius quod non potest derivari in dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>diametri poros, in quos devolvitur fluidum aliud datum? Id est
                        <lb/>annon particul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> minim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fluidum illud componentes, quod poris dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>diametri applicatum, per eosdem poros derivari non potest (per
                        <lb/>quos tamen effluit fluidum aliud datum iisdem applicatum) ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ioribus gaudebunt diametris quam sint diametri particularum
                        <lb/>minimarum fluidum aliud per dictos poros derivabile coagmentantium?</p>
<p><choice><abbr>Exempl.</abbr><expan>Exempli</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>gr.</abbr><expan>gratia</expan></choice> si Mercurius crudus effluere possit per datos poros ellipticos,
          <lb/>per quos effluere possit etiam aqua; nequeat autem ille efflue<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re per poros datos circulares, per quos aqua acta effluat. Annon
          <lb/>particul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> minim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Mercurium componentes maiores habebunt
          <lb/>diametros quam sint diametri particularum aquearum?
          <lb/>Theoriam fluidorum crassiorum, et subtiliorum prout ipse concipis,
          <lb/>si mihi saltem ex parte communicabis, maxime me tibi obstrictum ha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bebis.</p>
<p>Vale di<choice><orig><g ref="#uhat">û</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>, mihique favere ne desinas rogo: ego siquidem pro te, et
                    <lb/><choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nepote</rs> tuo omnes meas vires impendam ad hoc unus, aut alter
                    <pb facs="1078638" n="2r"/>
<lb/>ex vobis honorific<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> promoveatur ad Mathematum <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tavinam</rs>.</p>
<closer><salute>Tui Humillimus et <choice><abbr>Obsequentiss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Obsequentissimus</expan></choice>
<lb/>Servus</salute>
<lb/><signed><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person"> Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></signed>
<dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1714-07-21">21 Julii 1714.</date></dateline></closer>
